  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It could be a few meters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And deep a few meters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember one girl fell in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she climbed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as she was, with the shit over, she had to march through the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there they took her to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't let her wash herself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw her marching.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because they said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyway, until-- 'til the holes was not finished, so weak people fell in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it always was a whistle that you had to run in, because they was afraid [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] aeroplanes went through, they shouldn't see the people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So people had to run in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot-- a lot of people fell in in that-- how you say it?-- in that which wasn't filled yet with-- so in the hole.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The sewer, where the-- where the pipes should be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and when the whistle came, everybody had to run in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If somebody was weak, you couldn't jump over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You fell in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You fell in, the whistle came, and you've been in so they took you straight away to crematorium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And often I ran out quickly and I pulled the girls out and took them in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once I-- I was putting a girl in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The whistle came and I was there, so I was taking these-- all those girls on the truck to go to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But you see, this is unfortune-- unbelievables.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A woman, that woman who first didn't let us have the tea from beginning of camp, she wanted to be very friendly with me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But this time, those girls liked very much girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said that we don't know that and I hope you-- she doesn't mind.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
